{"tid":1714185,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"勞工處籲僱主就僱員上班安排作出彈性處理","createTime":"2019-11-13T00:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:20:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47acb0e2b4811576021319cd79cb9311a7a6a5ec","tid":1714185,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:07:26.000Z","msg":"勞工處呼籲僱主，應考慮今日交通及路面的情況，就僱員上班的安排作出彈性處理。這有助維持良好的勞資關係，並確保僱員安全及機構運作順暢。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，僱員如因路面交通或公共運輸服務狀況等問題而未能及時返回工作崗位，僱主應體諒僱員的情況並作出彈性處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府發言人表示，政府亦會同樣以體諒的態度處理政府僱員的情況。如僱員因交通問題而未能及時返回工作崗位，應盡快通知直屬上司，有關部門會作出彈性處理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491748-20191113.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491748-20191113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE90ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=5c6c04f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491748-20191113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6381b782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491748-20191113.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d812505d1be3225d6229c2b2ea1e7ac0baf19212","tid":1714185,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:08:04.000Z","msg":"死撚左啦<br />\n8點"},{"pid":"7c462e20a1171bb125233313bd75c083fabf2603","tid":1714185,"uid":338017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:08:51.000Z","msg":"彈你條撚"},{"pid":"11321dad651e2b57b79473f4c0241de7927e31cc","tid":1714185,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:09:00.000Z","msg":"林鄭好打得<br />\n繼續返工 社會一定要繼續run<br />\n我唔會屈服<br />\n你班賤民係我眼裡唔值錢<br />\n我既政治考慮凌駕於蟻民生命安全之上"},{"pid":"dd9493bd21ea137365243f3a3d57d2a057a8e658","tid":1714185,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:10:22.000Z","msg":"山竹級"},{"pid":"fdffe08103e0ba047a6647bafaa5e04